---
title: Italian-Style Portobello 'Ragu' with Rigatoni and Fresh Salad
description: All of that luscious deep, rich flavour a ragu needs, but without the meat! Packed with hearty mushrooms, tomatoes and garlic, this dish is a perfect go-to whenever you crave a heartwarming plate of red sauce pasta, for meat-eaters and veggie lovers alike!
